<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 15:14:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国与美军一起参加巴西军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-joins-brazilian-military-exercises-alongside-us-troops-2024-09-10/</link><description>巴西海军表示，中国军队本周将首次参加巴西武装部队举行的年度演习，与美国士兵一起训练。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 15:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-joins-brazilian-military-exercises-alongside-us-troops-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>卡迪什为沙特队赢得世界杯预选赛胜利，印尼队击败澳大利亚队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/indonesia-frustrate-australia-kadish-earns-saudis-world-cup-qualifying-win-2024-09-10/</link><description>周二，澳大利亚队在亚洲世界杯预选赛中又经历了一个令人失望的夜晚，格雷厄姆·阿诺德的球队被东道主印度尼西亚队以0-0逼平，而沙特阿拉伯队在最后时刻以2-1战胜了中国队。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/indonesia-frustrate-australia-kadish-earns-saudis-world-cup-qualifying-win-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促欧洲对中俄防务关系表示不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-europe-raise-disquiet-over-china-russia-defence-ties-2024-09-10/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二表示，美国敦促其欧洲伙伴更加有力地表达对中国与俄罗斯日益加强的防务合作的不安。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:33:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-europe-raise-disquiet-over-china-russia-defence-ties-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>RTX 看到劳动力挑战，探索中国供应商的替代方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-sees-labor-challenges-exploring-alternatives-china-suppliers-2024-09-10/</link><description>航空航天和国防巨头RTX的负责人周二表示，在COVID-19大流行之后，全球供应链仍然紧张，为航空航天工厂寻找合格的劳动力仍然是一个“巨大”的挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:13:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-sees-labor-challenges-exploring-alternatives-china-suppliers-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾战机执行训练任务时海上坠毁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-fighter-jet-crashes-sea-training-mission-2024-09-10/</link><description>台湾国防部和官方中央通讯社称，周二晚间，台湾空军一架幻影战斗机在台湾西北海岸坠毁，飞行员的搜救工作正在进行中，飞行员成功弹射逃生。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-fighter-jet-crashes-sea-training-mission-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国远景集团将在西班牙投资10亿美元生产绿色氢能机械</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-envision-invest-1-bln-spain-make-green-hydrogen-machinery-2024-09-10/</link><description>西班牙周二表示，已与中国远景集团签署协议，建设一座价值 10 亿美元的工厂，生产用于生产绿色氢气的机械。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 13:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-envision-invest-1-bln-spain-make-green-hydrogen-machinery-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>宝马因大陆制动问题下调 2024 年前景，股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-trims-2024-profit-margin-deliveries-forecast-2024-09-10/</link><description>由于主要中国市场的需求低迷以及大陆集团供应的制动系统出现问题，宝马周二下调了2024年的利润率预期，导致该汽车制造商的股价跌至近两年低点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 11:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-trims-2024-profit-margin-deliveries-forecast-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>券商报告显示，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪设定了更高的年度销售目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-sets-higher-annual-sales-target-brokerage-report-shows-2024-09-10/</link><description>摩根士丹利周一在一份报告中表示，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪今年的目标是销售 400 万辆汽车，建议将该公司今年早些时候设定的 2024 年销售目标上调 11%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:59:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-sets-higher-annual-sales-target-brokerage-report-shows-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>印度外交部长苏杰生表示“并未对中国业务关闭”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-foreign-minister-jaishankar-says-not-closed-business-china-2024-09-10/</link><description>印度外交部长苏杰生周二在柏林表示，印度并未“对中国业务关闭”，但问题在于该国在哪些领域与北京开展业务以及以什么条件开展业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-foreign-minister-jaishankar-says-not-closed-business-china-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙新政府继续禁止中国5G设备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/new-portuguese-government-keep-ban-chinese-5g-equipment-2024-09-10/</link><description>一位部长表示，葡萄牙中右翼政府将保留上届政府禁止电信公司在其 5G 网络中使用中国设备的禁令，尽管这一立场的预计成本是欧洲最严厉的之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:30:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/new-portuguese-government-keep-ban-chinese-5g-equipment-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国提议与欧盟谈判解决电动汽车关税争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-proposes-negotiations-with-eu-resolve-electric-vehicle-tariff-dispute-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国再次提出与欧盟委员会就解决经济和贸易摩擦进行谈判，以试图缓解即将对中国制造的电动汽车征收的惩罚性关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-proposes-negotiations-with-eu-resolve-electric-vehicle-tariff-dispute-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴股价因加入内地股市互联互通计划而上涨 4%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-shares-jump-4-its-addition-mainland-stock-connect-scheme-2024-09-10/</link><description>电子商务巨头阿里巴巴集团上个月将香港上市升级为主要地位，投资者对其在中国内地证券交易所上市表示欢迎，周二该股股价上涨 4.2%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-shares-jump-4-its-addition-mainland-stock-connect-scheme-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞标：电视辩论关注，中国焦虑，平静回归</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-10/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>普京称与中国举行海军演习是为了在太平洋对抗美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-teams-up-with-china-start-big-naval-drills-2024-09-10/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周二警告美国不要试图在亚洲击败莫斯科，俄罗斯和中国军舰举行了联合演习，这是自苏联时代以来最大规模的俄罗斯海军演习的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:28:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-teams-up-with-china-start-big-naval-drills-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国对43名足球运动员和官员进行终身禁赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-bans-43-soccer-players-officials-life-match-fixing-2024-09-10/</link><description>作为打击中国最受欢迎的体育运动之一的腐败行为的一部分，中国足协对假球和赌博行为进行了为期两年的调查，对 38 名足球运动员和 5 名俱乐部官员进行了终身禁赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-bans-43-soccer-players-officials-life-match-fixing-2024-09-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>